content:
Assign Case Feed to Users

After enabling Case Feed and creating a permission set, assign that permission set to users.

Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To change support settings:

Manage Cases
Customize Application

From Setup, enter Users in the Quick Find box, then select Users.
Select a user's name.
In the Permission Set Assignments list, click Edit Assignments.
Select the permission set you want in the Available Permission Sets list, and then click Add.
Click Save.

Set Up Cases for Salesforce Classic
Create Permission Sets for Case Feed
title: Assigning Service Cloud Case Feed to Users
